title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 4PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 4PM” game were:
8-9-1-9
(eight, nine, one, nine)
